rows.label: bf06140170_0010
rows.name:
Who are you, villain?! Is this some
underhanded Superbian trick?!

rows.label: bf06140170_0020
rows.name:
Wrong! But also right!
Truth is complicated!

rows.label: bf06140170_0030
rows.name: Anyhow, here is where Queen die.

rows.label: bf06140170_0040
rows.name:
If it look like Queen killed by
Superbia, me in the money again!

rows.label: bf06140170_0050
rows.name: That voice...

rows.label: bf06140170_0060
rows.name: Bahn, from the Avaritia Guild.

rows.label: bf06140170_0070
rows.name: Correct! Top marks for the Queen!

rows.label: bf06140170_0080
rows.name: But you were unseated as Chairman.

rows.label: bf06140170_0090
rows.name: Is not so easy to get rid of Bahn!

rows.label: bf06140170_0100
rows.name:
Trade Guild of Avaritia belong to Bahn!
Down to last screw, last drop of oil!

rows.label: bf06140170_0110
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Grr...

rows.label: bf06140170_0120
rows.name: Hold it, Bahn!

rows.label: bf06140170_0130
rows.name: You...Rex!

rows.label: bf06140170_0140
rows.name:
Meeeeh! Bahn not let Rex
interfere with plans!

rows.label: bf06140170_0150
rows.name:
Again and again... Bahn
not stand for this!

rows.label: bf06140170_0160
rows.name: Masterpon! That Artificial Blade!

rows.label: bf06140170_0170
rows.name:
It Sakura?! Mo-mo-mo... Tora feel
much greater power than before...

rows.label: bf06140170_0180
rows.name: Especially from mark on forehead!

rows.label: bf06140170_0190
rows.name: What's going on?!

rows.label: bf06140170_0200
rows.name: Wh-what's that?!

rows.label: bf06140170_0210
rows.name: Oho-ho-ho...

rows.label: bf06140170_0220
rows.name:
Even Emperor come straight to Bahn!
Convenient little moth to flame!

rows.label: bf06140170_0230
rows.name:
Come on, Bahn. Cut the bad-guy
talk and accept you've lost.

rows.label: bf06140170_0240
rows.name:
You know you won't get away with it,
what with all these witnesses here!

rows.label: bf06140170_0250
rows.name:
If Bahn simply kill
everyone then nobody blab!

rows.label: bf06140170_0260
rows.name: Victory of Bahn is assured...

rows.label: bf06140170_0270
rows.name: You know we can't let you do that!

rows.label: bf06140170_0280
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]*chortle*

rows.label: bf06140170_0290
rows.name:
You think you handle the power
of upgraded Great Sakura?!

rows.label: bf06140170_0300
rows.name: Things go very different this time!
